This is why the Magician epic was designed the way it is now.<br>
<br>
The epic spell (Summon Orb) summons an item (Orb of Mastery) with 1 charge (Manifest Elements) which is a 20 second cast.  The epic spell itself has a recast of 5 minutes.<br>
<br>
This in effect (ignoring the inventory shuffling) is an item with a cast time and recast time.<br>
<br>
The epic used to be something like a 20 second summon, with an instant click summon pet.  Verant deemed this too powerfull, and came up with the above solution. <p><FONT SIZE="3" COLOR=#FFFFFF FACE="Comic Sans MS, Sans-Serif, Courier New, Verdana, Arial, Helvetica">
